pageContext.claim: “We’ve created associations, millions of people are joining associations. Millions. That were formerly in Obamacare or didn’t have insurance. Or didn’t have health care. Millions of people.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is referring to an executive order but it has no force in law on its own and no one has yet joined these associations. The rules spelling out how the executive order would work had not been issued yet when Trump made these comments.
